              <path class="cring cring-2" d={contours.entries.charge.d}></path>
              <path class="cring cring-1" d={contours.entries.charge.d}></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="hintline">dwell to charge it — look away (pointer off) and it lets go</span>
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Concept>

    <Concept>
      <span class="concept-no">Gallery · data as participants <em class="truth truth-semantic">semantic</em></span>
      <h2>Records become bodies; relevance becomes gravity.</h2>
      <p>
        These rows aren’t markup — they’re <strong>data</strong>, bound to the field with
        <code>bindData(records, mapper, &#123; recipe: "search-relevance-field" &#125;)</code>. Each
        record becomes a body whose pull scales with its relevance; the field (behind the list) reads
        the data and the rows organize around it. Re-rank, and the bodies re-settle.
      </p>
      <p class="note">The same call powers a real search surface — data drives the field, the field renders the data.</p>
      <div class="binddata">
        <div class="bd-list" data-bd-list aria-label="Bound records"></div>
        <button class="agitate" type="button" data-bd-rerank>↯ re-rank</button>
      </div>
    </Concept>

